A Word About Our Breeders:

We are a small group of professional breeders. The owners of Pupworld have been raising puppies since 2015, they had clients come to them with frustration on not being able to find a quality breeder, Therefore the idea for the club was created. Animal welfare will always be our top priority and why we initially decided to come together as a community of breeders with just one listing platform. Working together as a team with just one website makes more sense than us all working independently.

Here at Pupworld our kennels are visited weekly by the ownerof Pupworld or an employee and spontaneously inspected by USDA so you have peace of mind knowing where you are adopting from. We do the leg work for you so the stress of potentially not adopting quality bloodlines from a responsible breeder is completely eliminated . The breeders are required to abide by the recommended protocol for vaccinations, deworming, and care for both the puppies and the parents.Also all parents are Genetic tested and have OFA’s done, Because of the strict guidelines that our breeders abide by, we are able to provide our 10yr health guarantee. This ensures you know we are willing to back each of our breeders and their bloodlines. Our goal is to ensure our clients have a selection of puppies to choose from while offering them a beautiful adoption experience with a knowledgeable team member.

The Pupworld Commitment

It is our promise to put your puppies welfare as our top priority.  That is why we have 24 hour on-site team members to care for your puppy everyday. We are committed to ensuring your new puppy is healthy and ready to join your family.
